name: Kinze 1121 Harvest Commander
description:
HARVEST COMMANDER 1121 DUAL AUGER GRAIN CART 1100 BUSHELS | 550 BU/MIN*  

Based on the proven and legendary 1050 dual auger grain cart, the 1121 is establishing its own place as a legend. 

The proven, straightforward dual auger design of the 1121 provides the key features necessary for efficient grain handling. The on-demand horizontal auger, optimum 1100-bushel capacity, tip spout control, and multiple undercarriage options deliver high value at a low cost of ownership. Robust construction, along with minimum driveline and track system maintenance, ensures an uninterrupted and productive harvest.

TRUE. BLUE. Advantage.

Cart capacity is based on #2 corn at 15% moisture (56lb test weight). Capacity may vary based on crop type, grade, moisture and other environmental factors. Capacity may vary between track and tire options. Bushels per minute may vary with moisture content of grain and/or PTO rpm.
